high_descs: move right towards the wall and then right towards the table at the right
pick up the knife from the table
turn left and move towards the sink and then right towards the fridge
open the fridge slice the piece of apple into four pieces  and then close the fridge
turn left and move towards the pavement and then left towards the microwave oven
drop the knife inside the microwave oven
turn around and move towards the fridge
take out a piece from the sliced apple
turn around and move towards the microwave oven
place the slice of apple in the microwave oven
take out the slice or apple from the microwave oven and move towards the fridge
place the slice of apple in the fridge
anns.task_desc: place a piece of cooked sliced apple in the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and go in front of the oven on the island's left side.
Take the yellow handle knife from the island counter.
Go around the island to the refrigerator.
Cut the apple in the refrigerator into pieces. Close the refrigerator door.
Turn around, go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator.
Take a piece of apple from the refrigerator.
Turn around, go to the microwave.
Put the apple in the microwave, turn on the microwave, take the apple from the microwave.
Turn around, go to the refrigerator.
Put the piece of apple in the refrigerator on the shelf above the apple and mug in the middle front of the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple in the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the left of the kitchen island, then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the yellow-handled knife from the countertop above the stove.
Go clockwise around the kitchen island to the fridge.
Cut the green apple int the fridge into thirds, leaving it in the fridge.
Turn left and go couterclockwise around the room until you are facing the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave, pointing left, and close the microwave.
Turn around and go clockwise, back to the fridge.
Take the back right third of the cut apple out of the fridge and close the fridge.
Turn left and go counterclockwise back to the microwave.
Cook the piece of apple in the microwave, remove it and close the microwave door.
Turn around and return counterclockwise back to the fridge.
Place the piece of apple on the center front of the top shelf of the fridge and close the fridge door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked piece of apple into the fridge.
